### EdgeCache control-plane API examples (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP).
@control = http://localhost:9000
@proxy = http://localhost:8080
@adminKey = dev-admin-key

### Health (public)
GET {{control}}/health

### Register an origin
POST {{control}}/origins
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "host": "dummy-origin", "baseUrl": "http://dummy-origin:8081", "healthCheckPath": "/health" }

### List origins
GET {{control}}/origins
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}

### Create a rule (120s TTL, 30s stale-while-revalidate)
POST {{control}}/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "pathPattern": "/products/*", "ttlSeconds": 120, "staleWhileRevalidateSeconds": 30 }

### List rules
GET {{control}}/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}

### Update a rule TTL (replace :id)
PUT {{control}}/rules/REPLACE_WITH_RULE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "ttlSeconds": 300 }

### Purge a URL fleet-wide
POST {{control}}/purge
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "pattern": "/products/1" }

### Purge a wildcard path
POST {{control}}/purge
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "pattern": "/products/*" }

### Purge audit log
GET {{control}}/purge/log
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}

### Stats for a path
GET {{control}}/stats?path=/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminKey}}

### ---- Proxy (data plane) ----
### Cache MISS then HIT
GET {{proxy}}/products/1

### Proxy metrics
GET http://localhost:9101/metrics

### Proxy readiness
GET http://localhost:9101/readyz
